# Walkthrough: Enterprise AI Orchestration

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    USER["n8n / User"] -->|POST /v1/webhook/n8n/async| MAIN["FastAPI"]
    MAIN --> GRAPH["Supervisor Graph"]
    GRAPH -->|tool calls| MCP["MCP Client"]
    MCP -->|SSE :8081| K["Knowledge Server"]
    MCP -->|SSE :8082| C["CRM Server"]
    MCP -->|SSE :8083| A["Automation Server"]
    K -->|Vertex AI SDK| RAG["RAG Corpus"]
    C -->|webhook_helper| N8N["n8n Webhooks"]
    A -->|webhook_helper| N8N
    MAIN -->|POST callback_url| USER
```

