## Changes Made

### Bug Fixes
| Fix | File |
|:----|:-----|
| [should_loop](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/app/graphs/supervisor.py#192-201) — `==` → `startswith("INCOMPLETE")` | [supervisor.py](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/app/graphs/supervisor.py) |
| Broken fallback import → `_fallback_workflow` | [main.py](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/main.py) |
| Rate limiter → `InMemoryRateLimiter(requests_per_second=3)` | [utils.py](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/app/utils.py), [llm_helper.py](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/shared/llm_helper.py) |

### Removed
- `get_deals` tool, `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM_GET_DEALS` env var, supervisor prompt reference
- Stale `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` / `N8N_WEBHOOK_AUTOMATION` fields from [config.py](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/app/config.py)
- `N8N_WEBHOOK_KNOWLEDGE_RAG` env var (Knowledge uses Vertex AI SDK directly)

### Refactored
- **Knowledge tools** → reverted to Vertex AI RAG SDK (deferred init)
- **Webhook proxy** → consolidated into [webhook_helper.py](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/shared/webhook_helper.py)
- **CRM tools** and **Automation tools** → now import shared `call_n8n_webhook`

